edu.iu.dsc.tws.comms.ucx

Class TWSUCXChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iu.dsc.tws.comms.ucx.TWSUCXChannel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TWSChannel

    public class TWSUCXChannel
extends java.lang.Object
implements TWSChannel
    This class uses UCX framework underneath to connect to the twister2's network of Worker processes. TWSUCXChannel leverages tags based communication of UCX to virtually create multiple communication channels between the workers based on the edge. The tag for each message is calculated as follows.

    tag = sendingWorkerId * tagWIdOffset + edge

    Since:
    0.5.0
